Class GNConverterTest

java.lang.Object
  de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.transform.germanet.GNConverterTest

public class GNConverterTest
extends java.lang.Object

Tests methods of GNConverter and the correctness of the UBY-LMF structure created by it.
Tests are made for GermaNet 7.0 data and UBY-LMF DTD version 0.2.0.
